Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:00.39,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:05.73,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:13.50,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.79,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:15.94,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.80,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I love the cakes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.32,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Do you come here often, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.87,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. This is Brother Jun's family's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:27.34,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:31.13,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, Yurika...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.63,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs45\blur0.7\c&HCECBE8&\fnHand Of Sean\b0\pos(640,132)}Shira                              {\c&HD2CDE7&}        yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:34.76,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,If you'd like, why don't you come over to my place to watch them practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:43.14,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.89,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}She hates me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:46.79,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,What is that, avant-garde?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:48.89,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Come on, Richie. Get your head on straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.30,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,How're we gonna have a session?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.65,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Everyone, Yurika is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.07,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Ritsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:03:01.57,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,didn't your dad tell you that outsiders aren't allowed down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:05.19,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yurika's a friend of ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.16,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,so I'm sure it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.73,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Well, Yurika, enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.50,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:12.75,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:16.75,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm just going to get some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.43,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:34.56,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.57,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,It's Richie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.72,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sentaro's sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.24,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sachiko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.17,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you playing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:46.74,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Yeah. All my friends are off at cram school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.32,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.96,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Then how about we play together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:53.82,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:57.89,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.48,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,It's not playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:00.59,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:07.10,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,That thing's ancient, so sometimes it gets ornery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:10.76,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,At times like this, a little magic is required.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.18,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Wow, Brother Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.61,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,How'd that get it to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:20.99,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.34,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Hello, is this the Children's Telephone Counseling Office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.16,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:28.87,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,See,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:33.62,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,there's this boy named Hashiguchi, and he's always mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.60,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,He hides my slippers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.13,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,pulls my hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.67,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,What do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.94,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hmm... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.51,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Y'know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:49.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,it may be that Hashiguchi actually likes you, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:54.41,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'd guess that he wants to be friends with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:56.87,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but he doesn't know how to express his feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.86,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,so he acts out like that without really thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.94,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,He does not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.02,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:07.45,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I made the girl that I like cry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.77,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I want to apologize to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.70,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but even if I do, I don't think she'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:17.71,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I don't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.71,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,That was my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.23,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.86,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I can't stay mad at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.52,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.90,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,There's something I have to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:47.15,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oddly enough, I've been going to the shop for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.07,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I had no idea it was your family's.
