Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.29,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,The coincidences just keep piling up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.67,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Even the name is similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.41,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.72,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,there's someone that I like already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:13.22,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,And right now, he's the only one I'd consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:16.57,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm flattered by your feelings for me, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.70,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm flattered, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:36.36,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.84,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.27,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.15,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Somethin' botherin' you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.00,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Here, this'll cheer you right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.45,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:50.18,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I said some terrible things to Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:54.20,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,He might not ever come back here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.98,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.00,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Sachiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:10.15,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Do you know who Ri'ko li—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:12.08,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sleepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.10,Default,Taichi,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.35,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.63,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,School starts again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:20.78,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I can't ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:25.46,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's impossible to talk about romantic stuff in this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.96,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie! It's been too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:32.18,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come over for practice during winter vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.49,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.39,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:45.31,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, the teacher told me to give this to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.31,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.58,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}My father finally came home,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.81,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}but everything seems so bleak right now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.41,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can't bring myself to talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:20.85,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.04,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen! What are you doing out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.90,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie! Get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.62,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:34.53,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,get your jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:36.20,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,We're gonna practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.70,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:44.03,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko is lonely without you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.63,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,C'mon, all you gotta do is stop by the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not going back there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.01,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:53.72,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:57.15,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Kaoru, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:03.35,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I thought I heard a loud noise up here a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.69,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.43,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:10.76,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Actually, I wanted to give you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:12.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.40,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It's from Shizu, our old housekeeper. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.79,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Shizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.43,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, that takes me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:21.14,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,She wrote about your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:27.79,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,We've had our problems over the years,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.67,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,but it seems that she happened to run into your mother in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:35.42,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,She got your mother's address and insisted I pass it on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.85,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,We split up when you were still little,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:42.18,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,so you might not remember your mom very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:48.19,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,But if you'd like to go see her, it's okay with me. Maybe on your next break...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.47,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I know it's kind of sudden and may leave you at a loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.84,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,but whether you go or not is entirely up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.90,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Well, I'll let you get back to your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:02.72,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.72,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,You should bring her some sweet rice treats as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:08.83,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I never said I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:10.93,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,You're not goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm just not up to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:15.67,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.97,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,You know where she is right now, and if you lose this chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.68,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,you'll regret it for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.32,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.35,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.40,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.48,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.37,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.35,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, you're hiding something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No, not particularly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:57.55,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Blue trains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.84,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,A blue train is basically
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:06.61,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,one of the limited express trains from Asakaze that has dedicated blue sleeper cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:12.69,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Did you know that the design of the front and back cars is different because they have to switch off being the lead car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.02,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:25.12,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, this is my first time traveling alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:30.11,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it's a journey to set me free from my heartache.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.62,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.88,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,You're late, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:37.13,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Y'know, it's a good thing I asked Maruo to get me a ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.05,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.40,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I felt like takin' a trip to Tokyo too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:44.26,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,so I'm comin' with!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:53.48,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really only came so I could have some alone time. To think things over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:57.94,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Man, travelin' an' frozen tangerines go together like bread an' butter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.42,Default,Old Woman,0,0,0,,I do have one more tangerine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:01.49,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, much obliged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.59,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,They taste so much better before they thaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:08.08,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit, Maruo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:10.70,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.85,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,how'd you afford this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.86,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.97,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I had money saved up from my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.46,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,And then I sold some old records.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.30,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You don't have nearly enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:25.49,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, if I can make it to Brother Jun's place, I'm sure it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:28.67,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he even try to think this through?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.23,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Here, this is yours, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.18,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko said the food in the dining car is probably expensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:41.21,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,so she made these for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:46.94,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Ain't you gonna eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.75,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,She's been worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.90,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,W-What's with all these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.40,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Is there a festival? Or a New Year's sale?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.90,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Tokyo Station is always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.32,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why don't you go sightseeing around Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.46,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I wanna see what your mom's like,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.45,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,so I'm comin' with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:37.46,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur1\yshad3\xshad1\fs25\fnBD Cartoon Shout\b0\fax-0.2\c&H709B83&\4c&H3A4134&\pos(650,76)}Blue Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.46,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,W-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.62,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,This is some workplace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.24,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-Wait, maybe I got the address wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.05,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.88,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, let's go in an' ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.20,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.71,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind about meeting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:53.14,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:56.21,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What're you talkin' about?! You came all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:58.64,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's better if I don't see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.38,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Even if I did, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.52,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:14.17,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,She says it's your mom's day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:16.70,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,And to come back here tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.21,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,So we'll come back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.95,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:23.34,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I say we relax a bit at Brother Jun's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:32.60,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Do you two have business with Katsuragi Junichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.02,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:36.02,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Well, there's no point in waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.43,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,He's been missing since last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.48,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:40.87,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:46.41,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Rumor has it he got in bad with some group and now he's in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:50.74,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Although it's possible he's just shacking up with some girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.66,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,That guy sure is popular with the college girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.26,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, that doesn't surprise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:58.22,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Right, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.66,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Nope, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.24,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Have you two come all the way from Kyushu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:12.39,Default,Hasegawa,0,0,0,,Well, let's make our guests from faraway Kyushu feel welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.51,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,With shochu and water...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.52,Default,All,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.04,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:19.94,Default,Hasegawa,0,0,0,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:26.73,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You wouldn't believe how stupid this guy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:32.04,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He's no end of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:36.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,When I'm with him, his stupidity rubs off on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:37.83,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.29,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,You're lucky to have such a good buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:43.45,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Buddy? Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.19,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Sounds like it's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.30,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Pretty rare to have a friend you can goof off with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.80,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Treasure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.80,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,Unlike love affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.07,Default,Okada,0,0,0,,friendship is for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:17.74,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.88,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Kaoru, that is you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.39,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.43,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What are you standing around like a scarecrow for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:27.25,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You'll catch cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:29.75,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Hurry up and come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.22,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.97,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I've never eaten fancy curry like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:42.16,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Go on, don't be shy. Just eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.25,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:43.98,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.44,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I like the way you shovel it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.73,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I've got a thing for men with a hearty appetite.{uh}{Huehuehue}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:54.76,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}She isn't at all like I figured she'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:58.84,Default,Kaoru and Mom,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.39,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.48,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Mother and son in perfect unison!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.80,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,S-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.18,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry... He has no manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.90,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Are you friends from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:14.87,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah... Well, more like, we play music together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:18.17,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He's a drummer and I play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:18.93,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:23.10,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaoru, you used to love it when your dad played the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:27.19,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,He would play and I'd sing along...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:31.94,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,And then, even if you were crying, you'd always stop and listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:36.45,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Such happy memories...{Fuck I don't know about this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.77,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.83,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't remember at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:44.71,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And anyway, Dad never likes to talk about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.53,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Of course he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:50.84,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Who would want to talk about a washout of a mother like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.94,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Looks like the rain has stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:58.99,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,so I'm gonna take a little stroll around Ginza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.31,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I think he wanted to give us some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.68,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,But eat before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.70,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's this curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.92,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's spicier than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.46,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:31.71,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,By the way, how's school going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.40,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.74,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Is there a girl that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.11,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh... Did it not work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.77,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,M-Mom...{MUM YOU'RE EMBARRASSING ME}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.80,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'd rather not talk about that right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:45.06,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What, I'm right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.56,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.60,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Well, just the idea of the baby boy I remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:55.14,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,who'd say "Mama" and make gurgling noises, having a broken heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.07,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You're in the heyday of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:05.54,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,A broken heart! Not bad, not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:09.71,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right! Like a lovesick puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.19,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}The more I laughed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.75,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}the more whatever had been building up inside me disappeared into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:20.14,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind emptied out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.43,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.07,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I thought you weren't gonna make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.68,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Mom, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.28,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.69,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's a jazz record.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.23,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,A song called "Lullaby of Birdland."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Listen and then sing along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.24,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll come back to visit you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.73,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,so until then, you should practice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:47.24,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,But this is in English, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.14,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I don't know the language at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.45,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You'll do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.48,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Just imitate what you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:57.30,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Jazz is best when sung by a lady with a husky voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.26,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll come back for sure, so please try, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.76,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Kaoru, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:09.27,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:10.83,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.27,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'd probably never see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.90,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That's what I told myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:33.08,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did my mom leave me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:40.16,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}The words I didn't have the heart to ask blurred away with the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:45.39,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her mouth formed the words, "I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:48.76,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shook my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.60,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm not sure she saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.10,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:57.07,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,That was heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.07,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:06.86,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Where were ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.41,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:21.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:28.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I waited for you on that road downhill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:41.98,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}Our promise to meet after school always held a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:51.28,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I was weak and distorted, and seemed to easily crack under pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:22:03.88,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}You were the one who gave me wings then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:12.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I wish I could say I love you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:23.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}while you're looking for a faint light in the sky at dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:35.54,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}The letter I wrote in the corner of my textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:43.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}will never reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:49.05,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}and nothing will ever change
